😔 When You Feel Regret or Failure:
Isaiah 43:18–19 – “Forget the former things; do not dwell on the past. See, I am doing a new thing!”

Romans 8:1 – “There is now no condemnation for those who are in Christ Jesus.”

😰 When You Feel Fear:
2 Timothy 1:7 – “For God has not given us a spirit of fear, but of power, love, and a sound mind.”

Isaiah 41:10 – “Fear not, for I am with you... I will strengthen you and help you.”

😢 When You Feel You’re Behind in Life:
Joel 2:25 – “I will restore the years the locusts have eaten.”

Philippians 1:6 – “He who began a good work in you will carry it on to completion.”

📖 Tip: Write these down. Speak one each morning and night. God’s Word is your daily weapon.
